Privacy Policy

Your privacy is important to us. It is Landezine Media d.o.o.’s policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our website, http://landezine.com/, and other sites we own and operate.

Your continued use of our website will be regarded as acceptance of our practices around privacy and personal information. If you have any questions about how we handle user data and personal information, feel free to contact us.
